Amelia Bayntun https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Amelia_Bayntun 0 Amelia Bayntun (31 March 1919 – January 1988) was an English stage and television actress. She was born in Bristol, on 31 March 1919 as Amelia Ellen Bayntun and died in Islington, London in January 1988, aged 68.
